## 💡 What I Learned

The biggest insight from this project was understanding the difference between **managed AI services** and **custom ML models**. With Rekognition I called a single API and got production-quality computer vision results in under 2 seconds — no training data, no model deployment, no cleanup. This is the core trade-off the AIF-C01 exam tests: use a pre-built service like Rekognition when your use case fits, use SageMaker when you need a custom model for a unique problem.

